tip.text: Set lunch meal is value for money !! Love it :)
The staffs are friendly and helpful 😊 Tends to be too busy in e mornings and ard 3 pm😅
Coffee was great and the ambience is awesome. Plenty of decent brunch menus such as egg Benedict, bagels etc, and not to forget -> free wifi + powerpoints which is great for a workaholic like me :)
The rib-eye was great !!! Some grill restaurants in town charge you 30 bucks for something worse...
